My Toilet Diary,

You want to hear a story
Not about your daily trip to the toilet....
The toilet is a great place as you say.  My fave part though is when I go to flush I wave goodbye to Trump, Pence, McConnell and Ryan.  Trump particularly likes it, he gets a freebie golden shower.

Can't imagine how they work out that logistic, cuz we know he's stubby as all get out. Maybe he has a sling to put his belly in.

One thing for sure, tho.  The women are wearing a blindfold - cuz that amount of white pasty blubber is enough to start anyone's gag reflex.
Scary is that i sat on the toilet as read this tweet, I felt a little exposed :)
Probably why Melainia doesn't care if he cheats.  Let somebody else deal with it.
This is why it costs him 250,000 to have sex with 2 women.  Look at those muscles in that younger body.  Can you imagine it now?,pic.twitter.com/zaMUylJMiE
